from wordcloud import WordCloud
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np
from PIL import Image
#point_dic에 단어 지정
point_dic = ['드라마','넷플릭스','엄마','카페','영화','영상','넷플릭스']
def color_func(word,**kwargs):
    if word in point_dic:
        return "hsl(35, 99%, 47%)" #색 지정
    else:
        return "hsl(25, 11%, 55%)" #색 지정

img_path = "c:/py_data/TV.jpg" #이미지 경로
cloud_mask = np.array(Image.open(img_path))


wordcloud= WordCloud(font_path = 'c:/Windows/Fonts/malgun.ttf',
                      colormap='Blues',
                     background_color="white", mask=cloud_mask, )


wc = wordcloud.generate_from_frequencies(cd)

plt.figure(figsize=(30,40))
#색 변경하기 
plt.imshow(wc.recolor(color_func=color_func))    #, interpolation = 'bilinear'
plt.axis("off")
plt.show()
